  <title>Ephemeris Tools</title>

  <section>
    <title>Using Ephemeris Tools in VE-Suite</title>

    <para>To use VE-Suite's ephemeris tools:</para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Load your visualization</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>In the VE-Xplorer menu, click Ephemeris Data</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>In the Date and Time tab, select the correct date and time and
        ensure that the box next to Display Ephemeris Data is checked</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>In the Latitude and Longitude tab, set the location by setting
        the latitude and longitude or by loading a location</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>To save a location:</para>

        <orderedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Set the longitude and latitude</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Click Save location</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter the new locations' name and click OK. That location
            will now be available to load in the future.</para>
          </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>
  </section>
